name: LoveStory
0:
”Alexa, open love story”
”Alexa, open love story and start a story”
”tell me my love story”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: love story
des:
Love Story is here to help you reignite the spark that brought you and your partner together. Simply answer a couple of questions and you are good to go. Enjoy!

- You MUST say 'stop' after answering Alexa's questions, so she can remember the answers for next time
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
